Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.11,CN,Mai,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.39,CN,Mai,0,0,0,,我們是旅行藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:23.29,CN,Warrior in Green,0,0,0,,啊 怪不得 真的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:27.09,CN,Warrior in Green,0,0,0,,對那個球的運用 還有輕鬆扛起我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:30.90,CN,Sayuri,0,0,0,,欸 我 我就只有力氣大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.71,CN,Warrior in Green,0,0,0,,非常厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.71,CN,Sayuri,0,0,0,,欸 哪哪哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:36.12,CN,Warrior in Green,0,0,0,,今晚準備住在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.52,CN,Mai,0,0,0,,欸 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.34,CN,Mai,0,0,0,,我們還沒有決定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:44.47,CN,Warrior in Green,0,0,0,,既然如此 請來我家留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.60,CN,Warrior in Green,0,0,0,,我家離這邊並不遠
